name: travaille dans le jardin / works in the garden / trabalha na horta, 2021
description:
With the series of photographs [quotidiennement / everyday / cotidianamente, 2021] _calkiel defies the biopolitics impressed on her body. With the help of photographer Franklin Lopes registers the performance. Each image is entitled by the action-place where it is performed.
4000x6000 300dpi
